messages.text: The Lord of Darkness is a lightweight
Or is partying with college kids your new calling?
I’ll return when I’ve won Sue’s soul
She didn’t sign before, so why now?
Then it wasn’t meant to be
Persephone says he misses his dad
He’ll be so happy when I have Sue!
I need to get out of here
It’s a good trait for Devils at first
But soon it becomes a brick wall
How many would’ve made deals, but you passed them for Sue??
When orientation is over, I’ll return
She’s talking to a Professor, looks like a crush
SHE SIGNED A PAPER FOR HIM
If that’s a soul contract, I’ll be pissed
If you possess Sue, it won’t count
I actually didn’t wait for you to tell me
Or a normal closet with brooms in it
Dude, don’t text. Just say it.
